  "texts": [
    "The identified applications, such as surveillance and patient experience analysis, are consistent with other reviews (10).",
    "However, our synthesis emphasizes the persistent gap between model performance on test datasets and their reliability on realworld public health data (15, 19).",
    "Models often perform less effectively in practice (36).",
    "Differences compared to earlier findings may stem from the rapid evolution of SA techniques, variations in the primary data sources used [with Twitter being prominent in the studies we reviewed (8, 12, 13, 25, 28, 31, 56, 58, 64, 73) ], and differing evaluation standards (19).",
    "For instance, while some researchers report high accuracy (29, 30), others find considerable disagreement between different SA tools and human judgments for complex health texts (19, 43)."
  ],
